        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Pasadena + La Cañada luxury</h4>
          <p><a href="/pasadena/">Pasadena</a> · San Marino · La Cañada · South Pasadena · Arcadia</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Ventura + Orange County luxury</h4>
          <p><a href="/thousand-oaks/">Thousand Oaks</a> · Westlake Village · <a href="/irvine/">Irvine</a> · Newport Beach · Laguna Beach · Corona del Mar</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>Related Asko and dishwasher-luxury pages</h2>
      <ul class="related-links">
        <li><a href="/brands/miele-dishwasher-repair/">Miele dishwasher repair (reference luxury) →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/brands/bosch-dishwasher-repair/">Bosch dishwasher repair (800 Series premium) →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/brands/thermador-dishwasher-repair/">Thermador dishwasher repair (BSH sibling) →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/brands/beko-dishwasher-repair/">Beko dishwasher repair (Arçelik family) →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/services/dishwasher-repair/">Dishwasher repair (service hub) →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/price-list/dishwasher-repair-cost/">Dishwasher repair cost guide →</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>Asko dishwasher repair, frequently asked</h2>
      {faqs.map(f => (
        <details class="faq">
          <summary>{f.q}</summary>
          <p set:html={f.a}></p>
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="book" class="cta-bottom">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>Asko XXL dishwasher service? Call the branch closest to your home.</h2>
      <p>Same-day appliance repair across Los Angeles, Orange, Ventura, San Bernardino, and Riverside counties. Residential diagnostic $89, waived with repair.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="float-call" aria-label="Call now">☎ Call {MAIN_PHONE}</a>
</Layout>

<style>
  :root { --red: #C8102E; --black: #0a0a0a; --gray: #f5f5f5; --border: #e2e2e2; --text: #1a1a1a; --muted: #6b6b6b; }
  body { color: var(--text); }
  .wrap { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
  .wrap.narrow { max-width: 820px; }
  h1 { font-size: 2.4rem; line-height: 1.15; margin: 12px 0 20px; color: var(--black); }
  h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 0 0 16px; color: var(--black); }
  h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 0 0 10px; color: var(--black); }
  h4 { font-size: 1.02rem; margin: 0 0 6px; color: var(--black); }
